00:03:44,406 --> 00:03:49,450
they said, well, you know, we're going to send you 10 Amiga 1000s, it's going to be

56
00:03:49,490 --> 00:03:55,155
some of the first Amigas that people receive and, you know, we really want to see your

57
00:03:55,235 --> 00:03:57,056
products on our machine.

