00:04:09,712 --> 00:04:14,675
keen to have on their machine. They didn't want baked beans on their machine, not in any form or

61
00:04:14,715 --> 00:04:21,721
way. And that's when the first moral question came to me in this boardroom. Do I lie? Do I say,

62
00:04:21,801 --> 00:04:25,263
yes, we're keen to put our products on their machine, or do I tell them the truth

