We sat on them.

68
00:04:42,089 --> 00:04:43,649
We made big bookcases out of them.

69
00:04:44,149 --> 00:04:46,590
You know, it was a generally fantastic time.

70
00:04:47,110 --> 00:04:50,271
But they kept phoning up and saying, we want a product, we want a product.

71
00:04:50,371 --> 00:04:52,332
And indeed, I did do a product.

72
00:04:52,472 --> 00:04:57,373
Not a game, because at that time, Commodore were absolutely fanatical that the Amiga 1000,

